  "detailed_description": "In <strong>Nudel Tag</strong>, challenge your friends to get the most tips, in a crazy ramen restaurant !<br>Find up to 4 controllers, to have the most fun, and see who is the best waiter in the house !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149280/extras/4c4b5478a6374015daa65ea35acba730.poster.avif?t=1759740062\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149280/extras/4c4b5478a6374015daa65ea35acba730.webm?t=1759740062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149280/extras/4c4b5478a6374015daa65ea35acba730.mp4?t=1759740062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You need to bring plates, from the chef, to the customers, easy, right ?<br>Well, unless the other waiters steal your plates and cash in your precious tips !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149280/extras/a1f10b1288c309cbdf92d40099497332.poster.avif?t=1759740062\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149280/extras/a1f10b1288c309cbdf92d40099497332.webm?t=1759740062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149280/extras/a1f10b1288c309cbdf92d40099497332.mp4?t=1759740062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>How can you get more chances to get some tips ? <br>Well, you can always spend what you got so far in bonuses <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149280/extras/94370c1422d1f757df80fb66a2db3c19.poster.avif?t=1759740062\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149280/extras/94370c1422d1f757df80fb66a2db3c19.webm?t=1759740062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1149280/extras/94370c1422d1f757df80fb66a2db3c19.mp4?t=1759740062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Have fun with this party game !",
